Kind: captions
Language: uz

00:00:00.350 --> 00:00:02.570
Kodni Internet
browserga ham yozish mumkin, biroq

00:00:02.570 --> 00:00:06.030
haqiqiy dasturchilar qanday imkoniyatlardan 
foydalanar ekan va bu kabi narsalar telefonga

00:00:06.030 --> 00:00:08.350
qanday tushirilar ekan deb o‘ylanarsiz balkim?

00:00:10.270 --> 00:00:12.730
Buning uchun zarur dastralarni o‘rnatish 
jarayoni ikki bosqichdan iborat.

00:00:12.730 --> 00:00:16.190
Dastlab Java Development Kit nomli 
majmuani o‘rnatish zarur

00:00:16.190 --> 00:00:19.240
undan keyin Android Studio o‘rnatiladi.

00:00:20.250 --> 00:00:23.300
Mening nazarimda Android Studio bu 
- ustaxona.

00:00:23.300 --> 00:00:26.320
Android ilovalar ishlab chiqishga 

00:00:26.320 --> 00:00:28.250
mo‘ljallangan maxsus ustaxona.

00:00:28.250 --> 00:00:31.930
Bunda ilovalar yaratishni 
yengillashtiradigan ko‘makchilar mavjud.

00:00:31.930 --> 00:00:34.900
Gap shundaki, ushbu ustaxona 
qanchalik zo‘r bo‘lmasin, 

00:00:34.900 --> 00:00:37.590
maxsus jihozlar to‘plami - Java Development Kit 
bo‘lmasa, u befoydadir.

00:00:38.670 --> 00:00:42.670
Shuning uchun eng avval 
Java Development Kitni o‘rnatib,

00:00:42.670 --> 00:00:44.900
ish uchun zarur maxsus jihozlarga ega bo‘lamiz.

00:00:44.900 --> 00:00:48.090
So‘ng Android Studio - ustaxonamizni o‘rnatamiz.

00:00:48.090 --> 00:00:50.735
o‘rnatish ishlarini shu tartibda 

00:00:50.735 --> 00:00:52.075
bajarish juda muhim.

00:00:52.075 --> 00:00:54.835
Agar jihozlar to‘g‘ri o‘rnatilmasa,

00:00:54.835 --> 00:00:56.315
ustaxonangizdan ham to‘g‘ri 
foydalana olmaysiz.

00:00:56.315 --> 00:00:59.525
Ushbu jarayon jami internet 
ulanish tezligiga qarab 

00:00:59.525 --> 00:01:02.255
30 daqiqadan 1 soatgacha vaqt olishi mumkin 

00:01:02.255 --> 00:01:03.115
Xo‘sh, boshladik!

